Mr. Lynmere he would find a very good place in one
of the plea&s;ure boats: but he an&s;wered he was ju&s;t
<PB N="97" REF="98">
come from them, and preferred going in the yacht.
Lord Pervil then only hoped the ladies would excu&s;e
