<P>&startq;No.&endq;</P>
<P>&startq;What the deuce! have you not examined the
larder? I have been looking over the three boats,
&mdash;there's nothing upon earth!&mdash;&s;o I came to &s;ee if
I could do any better here.&endq;</P>
<P>Halder vowed if there were nothing to eat, he
would &s;ooner jump over board, and &s;wim to &s;hore,
than go &s;tarving on.</P>
<P>&startq;Starving?&endq; &s;aid Mr We&s;twyn, &startq;why I &s;aw,
my&s;elf, &s;everal ba&s;kets of provi&s;ions taken into each
